item.title: ET
item.description: score:85 Chances: Energy Transfer LP reported higher adjusted earnings for the fourth quarter of 2023 and expects earnings to grow in 2024. The company expects its 2024 adjusted EBITDA to range between $14.5 billion and $14.8 billion, indicating a 7% increase from 2023.
